context:
* Full-time George Brown students are eligible for GO Transit student fares.
* Save on travel via GO Rail and GO Bus using the PRESTO card.
* Details of student discounts can be found on the GO Transit Student Savings website.
* Apply for the discount in person or online through the Go Transit Post-Secondary Student Discount website.
* Full time students must reapply for the discount every academic year.
* Contact GO Transit for information on passes or schedules: 1 (888) GET ON GO (438-6646), GO Transit website.
* Submit questions to George Brown College at ask.george@georgebrown.ca or call 416-415-2000, TTY: 1-877-515-5559.
* Winter 2024 program delivery information is available on the college website.
* Application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours and more can be signed up for on the college website.
* Contact numbers: 416-415-2000, TTY: 1-877-515-5559.
* Email address: ask.george@georgebrown.ca.
* Social Media Hub available on the college website.
* Information in the website is subject to change without notice.
* Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
